dct_description_sm: ganz neu vorgestellt von J.H. Coccejo.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of structures and settlements.
Appears in Weigel, Christophor, the Elder's Descriptio orbis antiqui. Nuernberg: Johann David Koehler, 1720. Plate 33.
